### <a id="tile-dev"></a> For <%= vars.product_name %> Partner Tile Developers

Tile developers package software services as _tiles_ for easy integration into <%= vars.product_name %>.
Platform operators install the tiles through a GUI, which lets the developers on the platform use the services.

Tile developers publish tiles on Pivotal Network, where services and tiles are available for download.

For tile developer documentation, see the [<%= vars.product_name %> Tile Developer Guide](https://docs.pivotal.io/tiledev/).
